&lt;p&gt;Second one is located in /etc/telegraf/ under name âtelegraf.confâ. My advice would to first to comment everything you donât need, and then uncomment stuff you need. In my case I needed Generic TCP listener (see picture).&lt;/p&gt;
















&lt;figure  id=&#34;figure-telegraf-config&#34;&gt;
